{"tid":2220311,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"9.6 12歲女童被警壓地 警由「制服」改字眼變「截停」","createTime":"2020-09-27T14:30:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T13:59:21.000Z","uid":240362,"like":9,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"ab69094392f405eb899a50896285a08e22a4ac7b","tid":2220311,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:30:38.000Z","msg":"繼8.31一周年拉跌孕婦一事後，警方再就9.6在旺角飛身撲跌兼騎身膝壓12歲女童事件「改口供」。油尖旺區議員余德寶稱接獲警方就事件的最新回覆，警方形容當日少女「可疑的舉措令到在塲（場）警員有必要以最低武力將該名少女截停」，更改9月初指「制服」少女的字眼，又稱事後曾安慰少女；但余引述其母親稱警方根本從無安慰女兒，反指摘她和兄長2人。余德寶批評警方謊話連篇、指鹿為馬。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200927/BKM7UYBH3NAYFIR6H3OWHCER6I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200927%2FBKM7UYBH3NAYFIR6H3OWHCER6I%2F&d=4SaXJ4tauImRU00LhBBHUj2x7fSflbdxuct7bsFM5Qs%3D&h=0d9e8a45\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200927%2FBKM7UYBH3NAYFIR6H3OWHCER6I%2F&h=a9be91f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200927/BKM7UYBH3NAYFIR6H3OWHCER6I/</a>"},{"pid":"eb03bfa87b57cff769db5bcbd9cd8fa0a550bcb8","tid":2220311,"uid":66798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:31:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7d0febb1a0f070d3f6c17d54da5c20efda2bf9f","tid":2220311,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb03bfa87b57cff769db5bcbd9cd8fa0a550bcb8","tid":2220311,"uid":66798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:31:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T14:31:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/